T02D1742:108b-0: @108b * // khva gdong ma srang mda' nag po zhes bya ba bzhugs /
T02D1742:108b-2: # // dur khrod 'jigs pa'i gnas nyid du //
T02D1742:108b-3: drag po bdud kyi nyi ma la ;
T02D1742:108b-4: / dkyil 'khor bca' dang thun rdzas bsog / lha mo srang mda' bca' byas la //
T02D1742:108b-5: bdag nyid gtso bo'i nga rgyal bya //
T02D1742:108b-6: sgo nga'i bya ba rdzogs pa dang //
T02D1742:108b-7: thun rdzas rnams la sngags 'di gdab //
T02D1742:108b-8: aom kh'a tar warti rbad dza dza /
T02D1742:108b-9: zhag bdun bsngags la thun rdzas 'di//
T02D1742:108b-10: dkyil 'khor byang gi phyogs su bzhag / de nas sgo nga'i steng nyid du //
T02D1742:108b-11: kha las lha mo bskyed byas la //
T02D1742:108b-12: gdug pa'i sngags rgod 'di yis gdab //
T02D1742:108b-13: he kh'a ta he badzra ma nu sarba thang rbad /
T02D1742:108b-14: sgo nga la ni zla phyed bar //
T02D1742:108b-15: drag po'i sems kyis gdab par bya //
T02D1742:108b-16: sgo nga brub khung lhung ba dang ;
T02D1742:108b-17: / gri gug dag gis brtol byas la //
T02D1742:108b-18: thun gyis brab cing sngags 'dis gsad //
T02D1742:108b-20: he mugs srog m'a ra ya thun ni rbad h'um h'um srog la he kha ta badzra rbad /
T02D1742:108b-21: bcu gcig bar du thun gyis brab //
T02D1742:108b-22: de nas mnan dang bsreg par bya //
T02D1742:108b-23: lha mo ngan song las la sbyar //
